Dia. 01 Five Space Shape
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 looks good, but after Black plays at 2 White can't live anymore.
\par Against White 3,\cf1\b  Black 4\cf0\b0  is a \cf1\b good move\cf0\b0  and it becomes the dead\cf2\b  five space shape\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par If White plays at 4 instead of 3, Black takes at A and it becomes eye vs. no eye situation.
\par
\par }
