Dia. 03 Correct Answer-Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's hane at 1 is the vital point for living.
\par The proverb says "\cf1\b there is death in the hane\cf0\b0 ". It changed into "\cf2\b there is life in the hane\cf0\b0 ".
\par
\par Black plays at 2 and 4, so it becomes sente bik for White.
\par So after White plays at 1 Black can't capture him anymore.
\par }
